    "Now we claim that y ′ is the minimum of {z ′ | h(y ′) ⊑ h(z ′)}, which implies h p (h(y ′)) = y ′.For suppose z ′ is a member of the set, so h(y ′) ⊑ h(z ′), and z ′ ⊑ y ′.",
